Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The secret of longevity
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8m0v
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Jul 1975
Summer heat in Manhattan. And a look at different approaches to ageing. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less